Package: axon-recorder
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Axon ROS Recorder
 Axon is a high-performance ROS recorder that writes sensor data
 to MCAP format with lock-free queues and plugin-based middleware
 support.
 .
 Features:
  - HTTP RPC API for remote control
  - Plugin-based middleware (ROS1, ROS2, Zenoh, UDP)
  - MCAP output format with compression
  - Crash-resilient state management
